HAI 1.4
    I HAS A cats ITZ A BUKKIT
    cats HAS A 0 ITZ "CEILING CAT"
    cats HAS A 1 ITZ "HAPPY CAT"
    cats HAS A 2 ITZ "LONG CAT"
    cats HAS A 3 ITZ "BASEMENT CAT"
    cats HAS A 4 ITZ "TACGNOL"

    I HAS A i ITZ 0
    IM IN YR loop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN 5
        VISIBLE "CAT " AN i AN ": " AN cats'Z SRS i
    IM OUTTA YR loop
KTHXBYE
